{"type":null,"faqId":38516,"title":"开启手套模式","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>开启手套模式，即使戴着手套也能对手机操作自如。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125556\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“智能辅助”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“手套模式”开关，开启手套模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3796","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448687000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":146,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"开启手套模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}